  "texts": [
    "They employed comparative prompts during the training phase and embedded a task perception feedback module in the enhancement process to make the restored image more realistic.",
    "In underwater object detection tasks, the limited amount of underwater image data poses a significant challenge.",
    "In response, researchers have proposed several approaches to address this problem and improve the detection capability of underwater object detection algorithms.",
    "For example, Zeng et al. (2021) proposed an underwater object detection algorithm based on Faster R-CNN and adversarial networks.",
    "By incorporating adversarial networks into the standard Faster R-CNN detection network for joint training, they increased the number of training samples and improved the network's detection capability."
  ],
